hadiths[52]{hadithnumber,text}:
2875,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey guzrey wo namaz padh rahey they, aap ney farmaya : ''aey abi ( suno ( wo ( aawaz sun kar) mutawajjeh huye lekin jawab na diya, namaz jaldi jaldi puri ki, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur kaha : السلام علیک ya Rasoolullah ! ( Allah key Rasool aap par salamti nazil ho), Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kaha : وعلیک السلام (tum par bhi salamti ho) Ubai ! jab mainey tumhen bulaya to tum merey paas kyon na hazir huye? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main namaz padh raha tha. aap ney farmaya : ''(ab tak) jo wahi mujh par nazil hui hai is mein tujhey kya ye aayat nahin mili « استجيبوا لله وللرسول إذا دعاكم لما يحييكم » ''aey eman walo ! tum Allah aur Rasool key kehney ko baja laao, jabke Rasool tum ko tumhari zindagi bakhsh chiz ki taraf bulatey hon'' (Al Anfaal : 24), unhoney kaha : ji haan, aur aainda Inshallah aisi baat na hogi. aap ney farmaya : ''kya tumhen pasand hai ke main tumhen aisi sura sikhaun jaisi sura na Torat mein nazil hui na Injeel mein aur na Zabur mein aur na hi Quran mein?'' unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ( zarur sikhaaiye ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''namaz main tum (Quran) kaisey padhtey ho?'' to unhoney Ummul Quran (Sura Fatiha) padhi. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key qabzey mein meri jaan hai. Torat mein , Injeel mein , Zabur mein (yahan tak key) Quranmein is jaisi sura nazil nahin hui hai. yehi saat aayaten hain aur yehi wo Qurane Azeem hai jo mujhey ata kiya gaya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik aur abu-Saeed bin Muallaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2876,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ginti key kuch lashkari bhejey (bhejtey waqt) un sey (Quran) padhwaya , to un mein sey har eik ney jisey jitna Quran yad tha padh kar sunaya. jab eik nau-umr nojawan ka number aaya to aap ney us sey kaha : aey falan ! tumharey sath kya hai yani tumhen kon-kon si suraten yad hain? usney kaha : mujhey falan-falan aur Sura Baqra yad hai. aap ney kaha : kya tumhen Sura Baqra yad hai? usney kaha : haan , aap ney farmaya : '' jaao tum un sab key ameer ho''. unkey shurfa mein sey eik ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! qism Allah ki ! mainey Sura Baqra sirf isi dar sey yad na ki ke main usey (namaz tahajjud mein) barabar padh na sakunga. aap ney farmaya : '' Quran seekho , usey padho aur padhaao. kyonkey Quran ki misal us shakhs key liye jisney usey seekha aur padha, aur is par amal kya us thaili ki hai jis mein mushk bhari hui ho aur chaaron taraf uski khushbu phel rahi ho, aur us shakhs ki misal jisney usey seekha aur so gaya uska ilm uskey seeney mein band raha. us thaili ki si hai jo mushk bhar kar seal-band kar di gaee ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. - is hadees ko Les bin Saad ney Saeed Maqbari sey , aur Saeed ney abu-Ahmad key azad karda ghulam ata sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kya hai, aur unhoney us riwayat mein Abu-Hurera ka zikr nahin kya."
2877,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' apney gharon ko qabristaan na banao . wo ghar jis mein Sura Baqra padhi jati hai is mein shetan dakhil nahin hota ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2878,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' har chiz ki eik choti hoti hai padhi. aur Quran ki choti Sura Baqra hai, is Sura main eik aayat hai ye Quran ki sari aayaton ki sardar hai aur ye aayat aayatal-kursi hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Hakim bin Juber ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- Hakim bin Juber key barey mein Shoba ney kalam kya hai aur unhen zaeef qarar diya hai."
2879,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Sura momin ki) ibtidaai teen aayaat ( « Ha-Mim » sey « إليه المصير » tak aur aayatal-kursi subh hi subh (bedaar honey key baad hi) padhi to un dono key zariey Sham tak uski hifazat ki jaeygi, aur jisney un dono ko Sham hotey hi padha to unkey zariey uski subh honey tak hifazat ki jaeygi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr bin abi Muleka key hafzey key silsiley mein kalam kya hai, 3- Zarara bin Musab ka pura naam Zarara bin Musab bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf hai, aur wo Abu-Musab madni key dada hain."
2880,"unka apna eik ihata tha is mein khajuren rakhi hui thin. jin aata tha aur is mein sey utha ley jata tha, unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baat ki shikayat ki. aap ney farmaya : '' jaao jab dekho ke wo aaya huwa hai to kaho : Bismillah ( Allah key naam sey) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baat maan '' , Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey pakad liya to wo qasmen kha kha kar kehney laga ke mujhey chhod do, dobara wo aisi harkat nahin kerega, chunanche unhoney usey chhod diya . phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to aap ney un sey puchha , '' tumharey qaidi ney kya kya ?'' unhoney kaha : usney qasmen khaain ke ab wo dobara aisi harkat na kerega. aap ney farmaya : '' usney jhoot kaha : wo jhoot bolney ka aadi hai'' , Raavi kehtey hain : unhoney usey dobara pakda , usney phir qasmen khaeyn ke usey chhod do , wo dobara na aayega to unhoney usey ( dobara ( chhod diya, phir wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to aap ney puchha : ''tumharey qaidi ney kya kya?'' unhoney kaha : usney qism khai ke wo phir lot kar na aayega . aap ney farmaya : ''us ney jhoot kaha, wo to jhoot bolney ka aadi hai''. ( phir jab wo aaya ( to unhoney usey pakad liya , aur kaha : ab tumhen Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley jaey baghair na chhodunga. usney kaha : mujhey chhod do , main tumhen eik chiz yani aayatal-kursi bata raha hun . tum usey apney ghar mein padh liya karo. tumharey qarib shetan na aayega aur na hi koi aur aayega'', phir Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to aap ney un sey puchha : '' tumharey qaidi ney kya kya ? '' to unhoney aap ko wo sab kuch bataya jo usney kaha tha. aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us ney baat to sahih kahi hai, lekin wo hai pakka jhoota''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2881,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney raat mein Sura Baqra ki aakhiri do aayaten padhin wo uskey liye kafi ho gaeen''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2882,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney zamin o aasman paida karney sey do hazar saal pehley eik kitab likhi, is kitab ki do aayaten nazil kin aur unhen dono aayaton par Sura Baqra ko khatam kya, jis ghar mein ye dono aayaten (musalsal) teen raaten padhi jaeyngi mumkin nahin hai ke shetan us ghar key qarib aa sakey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2883,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Quran aur Quran wala jo duniya mein Quran par amal karta hai dono ayengey un ki peshwai Sura Baqra aur Aale-Imran kerengi ''. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un dono Suraton ki teen misalen din, uskey baad phir main un Suraton ko na bhoola. aap ney farmaya : '' goya ke wo dono chhatriyan hain, jinkey bich mein shigaaf aur phatan hain, ya goya ke wo dono kaali badliyan hain, ya goya ke wo saf basta chidiyon ka sayeban hain, ye dono suraten apney padhney walon aur un par amal karney walon ka lad-jhagad kar difaa aur bachaaw kar rahi hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Barida aur abu-Umama sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- is hadees ka baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik maana o mafhoom ye hai ke Quran padhney ka sawab aayega. is hadees aur is jaisi deegar ahadees ki baaz ehle-ilm ney yehi tafseer ki hai ke Quran padhney ka sawab aayega , nawaas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, mufassereen ki us tafseer ki daleel aur uska sabut milta hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key is qol « وأهله الذين يعملون به في الدنيا » mein ishara hai ke Quran key aaney sey murad unkey aamal ka sawab hai."
2884,wo Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees (ما خلق الله من سماء wala أرض أعظم من آية الكرسي) ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : aayatal-kursi ki fazilat is wajeh sey hai ke ye Allah ka kalam hai aur Allah ka kalamullah ki makhluq yani aasman o zamin sey badh kar hai.
2885,"eik aadmi Sura Kahaf padh raha tha ke usi doran usney apney chopaey ( sawari ( ko dekha ke wo (apney khoontey par) naachney aur uchal kood karney laga . usney nazar ( idhar-udhar ( daudaai to usey eik badli si nazar aai , phir wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , aur us (waqiey) ka aap sey zikr kya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ye sakeenat ( tamaniyat ( thi jo Quran ki wajeh sey ya Quran padhney par nazil hui ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usaid bin Huzer sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2886,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai teen aayaat padhin wo dajjaal key fitney sey bacha liya gaya'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2887,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' har chiz ka eik dil hota hai, aur Quran ka dil Sura Yasin hai. aur jisney Sura Yasin padhi to Allah Taala uskey liye uskey padhney key siley mein das martaba Quran shareef padhney ka sawab likhey ga ''. is sanad sey bhi ye sabiqa hadees ki tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum sirf Humed bin Abdur-Rehman ki riwayat sey jantey hain. aur ehale-Basra Qatada ki riwayat ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. aur Harun abu Muhammad Shekh majhool hain. padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq sey bhi riwayat hai, aur ye riwayat sanad key aetbar sey sahih nahin hai. 4- iski sanad zaeef hai aur is baab mein Abu-Hurera sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2888,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sura «Dukhan» kisi raat mein padhey wo us haal mein subh kerega ke uskey liye sattar hazar farishtey duaaey maghfirat kar rahey hongey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 3- umr bin abi Khasam zaeef qarar diye gaey hain, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke wo munkirul-hadees hain."
2889,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs Juma ki raat mein «Dukhan» padheyga usey bakhsh diya jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Hisham Abul-Miqdam zaeef qarar diye gaey hain, 3- Hasan Basri ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai, Ayub, Yunus bin Ubaid aur Ali bin Zaid ney aisa hi kaha hai."
2890,"Sahaba mein sey kisi ney apna khema eik qabr par nasab kar diya aur unhen malum nahin huwa ke wahan qabr hai, ( unhoney aawaz suni (us qabr mein koi insan Sura « تبارك الذي بيده الملك » padh raha tha, yahan tak ke usney puri Sura khatam kar di . wo Sahib Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye phir aap sey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey apna khema eik qabr par nasab kar diya, mujhey guman nahin tha ke us jagah par qabr hai. magar achcha kya sunta hun ke us jagah eik insan Sura Mulk padh raha hai aur padhtey huye usney puri Sura khatam kar di. aap ney farmaya : « هي المانعة » '' ye Sura Maaniaa hai, ye najat deney wali hai, apney padhney waley ko azabe-qabr sey bachaati hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2891,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Quran ki tees aayaton ki eik Sura ney eik aadmi ki shafaat ( sifarish ( ki to usey bakhsh diya gaya, ye Sura « تبارك الذي بيده الملك » hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2892,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab tak (الم تنزيل) aur « تبارك الذي بيده الملك » padh na letey sotey na they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko kaee eik riwayaton ney Les bin abi saleem sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai, 2- Mughira bin Muslim ney abu-Zubair sey, aur abu-Zubair ney Jabir key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- zuhair riwayat kartey huye kehtey hain : mainey abu-Zubair sey kaha : aap ney Jabir sey suna hai, to unhoney yehi hadees bayan ki ? abu-Zubair ney kaha : mujhey Safwan ya ibn Safwan ney uski khabar di hai. to un zuhair ney abu-Zubair sey Jabir key wastey sey is hadees ki riwayat ka inkar kya hai."
2893,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Sura « إذا زلزلت الأرض » Sura padhi to usey aadha Quran padhney key barabar sawab milega, aur jisney Sura « قل يا أيها الكافرون » padhi to usey chothai Quran padhney key barabar sawab milega, aur jisney Sura « قل هو الله أحد » padhi to usey eik tihai Quran padhney ka sawab milega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum usey kisi aur sey nahin sirf unhen Hasan bin Muslim ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2894,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « إذا زلزلت » ( sawab mein) aadhey Quran key barabar hai, aur « قل هو الله أحد » tihai Quran key barabar hai aur « قل يا أيها الكافرون » chothai Quran key barabar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Yaman bin Mughira ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain."
2895,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney eik Sabab sey farmaya : ''aey falan! kya tum ney shaadi kar li? '' unhoney kaha : nahin, qism Allah ki ! Allah key Rasool! nahin ki hai, aur na hi merey paas aisa kuch hai jis key zariey main shaadi kar sakun. aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas Sura « قل هو الله أحد » nahin hai? '' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, merey paas hai. aap ney farmaya : '' Sura « قل هو الله أحد » sawab main eik tihai Quran key barabar hai ''. aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas Sura Nasr nahin hai? '' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, ( hai) aap ney farmaya : '' ye eik chothai Quran hai'' , aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas Sura « قل يا أيها الكافرون » nahin hai? '' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin .) hai) aap ney farmaya : '' ( ye ( chothai Quran hai ''. aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas Sura « إذا زلزلت الأرض » nahin hai? '' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ( hai) aap ney farmaya : '' ye eik chothai Quran hai'' , aap ney farmaya : '' tum shaadi karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2896,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tum mein sey koi is baat sey bhi aajiz hai ke raat main eik tihai Quran padh daley? (aap ney farmaya) jisney « الله الواحد الصمد » padha (yani Sura Ikhlas padhi) usney tihai Quran padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- hum kisi ko nahin jantey jisney zyada ki riwayat sey behtar usey riwayat kya ho, aur un ki riwayat par un ki mutaabiat Israel , Fuzel bin ayaaz ney ki hai. Shoba aur unkey ilawa kuch doosrey logon ney ye hadees mansoor sey riwayat ki hai aur un sabhon ney is mein iztirab ka sey kaam liya, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abu-Darda, abu Saeed Khudri, Qatada bin Noman, Abu-Hurera , Anas , ibne-Umar aur abu-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2897,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath aaya , aap ney wahan eik aadmi ko « قل هو الله أحد الله الصمد » padhtey huye suna, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wajib ho gaee ''. mainey kaha : kya chiz wajib ho gaee? aap ney farmaya : '' jannat (wajib ho gaee) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is hadees ko sirf Malik bin Anas ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2898,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs har din do so martaba « قل هو الله أحد » padheyga to qarz key siwa uskey pachas saal tak key gunah mita diye jaeyngey''.
2899,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « قل هو الله أحد » eik tihai Quran key barabar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2900,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum sab ikhattey ho jaao kyonkey main tum sab ko tihai Quran padh kar sunaney wala hun.''  chunanche aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki. is pukar par jo bhi pahunch saka jama ho gaya, phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bahar tashrif laye, Sura « قل هو الله أحد » padhi aur (hujrae shareef mein) wapis chaley gaey. to baaz Sahaba ney che-mein-goiyaan kartey huye kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya tha : main anqarib tumhen tihai Quran padh kar sunaaunga, mera khayal ye hai ke aisa us wajeh sey huwa hai ke aasman sey koi khabar (koi ittilaa) aa gaee hai, phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kamrey sey bahar nikley aur farmaya : ''main ney kaha tha main tumhen tihai Quran padh kar sunaaunga to sun lo ye Sura « قل هو الله أحد » tihai Quran key barabar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2901,"Masjide Qubaa main eik Ansari shakhs un ki imaamat karta tha, aur uski aadat ye thi ke jab bhi wo irada karta ke koi sura namaz mein padhey to usey padhta lekin is sura sey pehley « قل هو الله أحد » puri padhta , phir uskey sath dusri sura padhta , aur wo ye amal har rakat mein karta tha. to uskey sathiyon (namaaziyon) ney us sey (is mauzoo par) baat ki, unhoney kaha : aap ye sura padhtey hain phir aap khayal kartey hain ke ye to aap key liye kafi nahin hai yahan tak ke dusri sura (bhi) padhtey hain, to aap ya to sirf isey padhein, ya isey chhod den aur koi dusri sura padhein, to unhoney kaha : main isey chhodney wala nahin, agar aap log pasand karen ke main isey padhney key sath sath imaamat karun to imaamat karunga aur agar aap log iskey sath imaamat kaarna pasand nahin kartey to main aap logon (ki imaamat) ko chhod dunga. aur logon ka haal ye tha ke unhen apnon mein sab sey afzal samajhtey they aur napasand kartey they ke unkey siwa koi doosra un ki imaamat karey, chunanche Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab un logon key paas aaye to unhoney aap ko sari baat batai. aap ney farmaya : ''aey falan ! tumharey sathi jo baat keh rahey hain, is par amal karney sey tumhen kya chiz rok rahi hai aur tumhen kya chiz majbur kar rahi hai ke har rakat main tum is sura ko padho?''  unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main isey pasand karta hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''iski mohabbat tumhen jannat mein ley jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib sahih hai aur ye Ubedullah bin umr ki riwayat sey hai jisey wo Sabit sey riwayat kartey hain."
2902,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney mujh par aisi aayaat nazil ki hain jaisi ( kabhi ( nahin dekhi gaee hain, wo ye hain : « قل أعوذ برب الناس » aakhir Sura tak aur « قل أعوذ برب الفلق » aakhir Sura tak ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2903,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey hukm diya ke har namaz key baad muawwizatain padha karun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2904,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran padhta hai aur Quran padhney mein maharat rakhta hai wo buzurg pakbaz farishton key sath hoga, aur jo shakhs Quran padhta hai aur badi mushkil sey padh paata hai, padhna usey bahut shaaq guzartaa hai to usey dohra ajr milega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2905,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Quran padha aur usey puri tarah hifz kar liya, jis chiz ko Quran ney halal thehraya usey halal jana aur jis chiz ko Quran ney haram thehraya usey haram samjha to Allah usey is Quran key zariey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga. aur uskey khaandaan key das aisey logon key barey mein is (Quran) ki sifarish qubul karega jin par jahannam wajib ho chuki hogi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- iski sanad sahih nahin hai. 3- Hafs bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) hadees mein zaeef qarar diye gaey hain."
2906,"masjid mein gaya to kya dekhta hun ke log gap-shap aur qisse kahaniyon mein mashghool hain, main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas pahuncha. mainey kaha : Ameerul-Momineen ! kya aap dekh nahin rahey hain ke log faaltu baaton mein padey huye hain?  unhoney kaha : kya waqae wo aisa kar rahey hain? mainey kaha : haan , unhoney kaha : magar mainey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''anqareeb koi fitna barpa hoga.''  mainey kaha is fitna sey bachney ki surat kya hogi? Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''kitabullah , is main tum sey pehley key logon aur qomon ki khabren hain aur baad key logon ki bhi khabren hain, aur tumharey darmiyan key umoor aur maamlat ka hukm aur faisla bhi is mein mojud hai, aur wo do tok faisla karney wala hai, hansi mazaq ki chiz nahin hai. jisney isey sarkashi sey chhod diya Allah usey tod dega aur jo isey chhod kar kahin aur hidayat talash kerega Allah usey gumrah kar dega. wo (Quran) Allah ki mazbut rassi hai ye wo hikmat bhara zikr hai, wo sidha raasta hai, wo hai jiski wajeh sey khuwahishen idhar udhar nahin bhatak paati hain, jiski wajeh sey zabanen nahin ladkhadaatin, aur ulama ko (chahey kitna hi isey padhein) ji nahi bharta, iskey baar-baar padhney aur takraar sey bhi wo puraanaa (aur be maza) nahin hota. aur iski anokhi (aur qeemti) baaten khatam nahin hotin, aur wo Quran wo hai jisey sun kar jin khamosh na reh sakey balke pukar uthey : hamney eik ajeeb (anokha) Quran suna hai jo bhalai ka raasta dikhata hai, to hum is par eman ley aaye, jo uskey mutabiq boleyga uskey mutabiq amal kerega usey ajr aur sawab diya jaeyga. aur jisney iskey mutabiq faisla kiya usney insaf kiya aur jisney iski taraf bulaya usney  sidhey raastey ki hidayat di. Aa'war ! in achchhi baaton ka khayal rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- iski sanad majhool (anjaan) hai. 3- Haris key barey mein kalam kiya gaya hai."
2907,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey behtar wo shakhs hai jo Quran seekhey aur sikhlaaye.'' abu-Abdur-Rehman Sulami (Raavi hadees) kehtey hain : yehi wo chiz hai jisney mujhey apni is nashist gaah (musnad) par bitha rakha hai, Usman key zamaney mein Quran ki taalim deni shuru ki (aur detey rahey) yahan tak Hujjaaj bin Yusuf key zamaney mein ye silsila chalta raha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2908,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sab sey behtar ya tum mein sab sey afzal wo shakhs hai jo Quran seekhey aur sikhlaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi aur kaee dusron ney isi tarah basanad (سفيان الثوري an علقمة بن مرثد an أبي عبدالرحمٰن an عثمان an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, 3- Sufiyan iski sanad mein Saad bin Ubeda ka zikr nahin kartey hain, 4- Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney ye hadees basanad (سفيان وشعبة an علقمة بن مرثد an سعد بن عبيدة an أبي عبدالرحمٰن an عثمان an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki. hum sey bayan kya usey Muhammad bin Bashaar ney , wo kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kya Yahya bin Saeed ney Sufiyan aur Shoba key wastey sey ."
2909,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sab sey behtar wo shakhs hai jo Quran seekhey aur sikhlaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ko hum Ali bin abi Talib ki riwayat sey jisey wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
2910,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kitabullah ka eik harf padha usey uskey badley eik neki milegi, aur eik neki das guna badha di jaeygi, main nahin kehta « Alif-Lam-Mim » eik harf hai, balke «Alif» eik harf hai, « Lam » eik harf hai aur « Mim » eik harf hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi ibne-Masood sey riwayat ki gaee hai, 2- is hadees ko Abul-Ahwas ney ibne-Masood sey riwayat kya hai. baaz ney isey marfooan riwayat kya hai aur baaz ney isey ibne-Masood sey moqufan riwayat kya hai, 3- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2911,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala kisi bandey ki koi baat itni ziyada tawajjoh aur yaksu ho kar nahin sunta jitni do rakatein padhney waley bandey ki sunta hai, aur banda jab tak namaz padh raha hota hai uskey sar par neki ki barish hoti rehti hai, aur bandey Allah azz-w-jall sey) kisi chiz sey) utna qarib nahin hotey jitna us chiz sey jo uski zaat sey nikli hai'', abu-Nazar kehtey hain : aap us qol sey Quran murad letey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Bakr bin Khunes key barey mein ibne-Mubarak ney kalam kya hai aur aakhir Amr yani baad mein (unkey zaeef honey ki wajeh sey) un sey riwayat kerni chhod di thi, 3- ye hadees Zaid bin Irtaat key wastey sey Juber bin Nufer sey marvi hai unhoney Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal tareeq sey riwayat ki hai."
2912,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum Allah ki taraf ruju karney key liye Quran sey badh kar koi aur zariey nahin paa saktey ''.
2913,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo shakhs jis key dil mein Quran ka kuch hissa yad na ho wo wiran ghar ki tarah hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2914,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (qiyamat key din) sahibe-Quran sey kaha jaeyga : ( Quran ( padhta ja aur) bulandi ki taraf ( chadhta ja. aur wesey hi thehar thehar kar padh jis tarah to duniya mein thehar thehar kar tarteel key sath padhta tha. pas teri manzil wo hogi jahan teri aakhiri aayat ki tilawat khatam hogi '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2915,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Quran qiyamat key din pesh hoga pas kahega : aey merey rab ! usey ( yani sahibe-Quran ko) joda pahna, to usey karaamat ( izzat o sharafat (ka taaj pehnaya jaeyga. phir wo kaheyga : aey merey rab! usey aur dey, to usey karaamat ka joda pehnaya jaeyga. wo phir kaheyga : aey merey rab us sey razi o khush ho ja, to wo us sey razi o khush ho jaeyga. us sey kaha jaeyga padhta ja aur chadhta ja, terey liye har aayat key sath eik neki ka izafa kya jata rahega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2916,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat key nek aamal key ajr o sawab merey samney pesh kiye gaey yahan tak ke us tinkey ka sawab bhi pesh kya gaya jisey aadmi masjid sey nikal kar phenk deta hai. aur mujh par meri ummat key gunah ( bhi) pesh kiye gaey to mainey koi gunah us sey badh kar nahin dekha ke kisi ko Quran ki koi Sura ya koi aayat yad ho aur usney usey bhula diya ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 3- mainey is hadees ka tazkira Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey kya to isko wo pehchan na sakey aur unhoney is hadees ko gharib qarar diya, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney ye bhi kaha ke main nahin janta ke Muttalib bin Abdullah ki kisi Sabab Rasool sey sama Sabit hai, siwaye Muttalib key us qol key ke mujh sey us shakhs ney riwayat ki hai jo Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki haazirin mein mojud tha, 5- mainey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman ( Darmi ( ko kehtey huye suna hai ke hum Muttalib ka samaa, kisi Sabab Rasool sey nahin jantey , 6- Abdullah ( Darmi ye bhi) kehtey hain : Ali bin Madini is baat ka inkar kartey hain ke Muttalib ney Anas sey suna hai."
2917,"wo eik qissa bhale hi key paas sey guzrey jo Quran padh raha tha ( padh kar) wo maangney laga . to unhoney (إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون) padha , phir kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna hai jo Quran padhey to usey Allah hi sey maangna chahiye . kyonkey anqarib kuch log aisey ayengey jo Quran padh-padh kar logon sey maangengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, iski sanad wesi qawi nahin hai, 2- Mehmood bin Ghelaan kehtey hain : ye khaisma Basra hain jin sey Jabir Jaafi ney riwayat ki hai. ye khaisma bin Abdur-Rehman nahin hain. aur khaisma Shekh Basra hain unki kunniyat Abu-Nasar hai aur unhoney Anas bin Malik sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain. aur Jabir Jaafi ney bhi khaisma sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain."
2918,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Quran ki haram ki hui chizon ko halal jana wo Quran par eman nahin rakhta ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai, Wakee ki riwayat mein Wakee sey ikhtilaf kya gaya hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Abu-Farwa kehtey hain : Yazeed bin Sanan Rahawi ki riwayat leney mein koi harj nahin hai. siwaye us riwayat key jisey unkey betey Muhammad un sey riwayat kartey hain, isliye ke wo unsey munkar riwayat kartey hain, 3- Muhammad bin Yazeed bin Sanan ney apney baap sey ye hadees bhi riwayat ki hai aur iski sanad mein itna izafa kya hai : (عن مجاهد an سعيد بن المسيب an صهيب) Muhammad bin Yazeed ki riwayat ki kisi ney mutaabiat nahin ki, wo zaeef hain, aur abul-Mubarak eik majhool shakhs hain."
2919,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : '' buland aawaz sey Quran padhney wala aisa hai jaisa khuley aam sadqa deney wala , aur aahisatagi o khamoshi sey Quran padhney wala aisa hai jaisey chupa kar sadqa deney wala ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is hadees ka maana o matlab ye hai ke jo shakhs aahisatagi sey Quran padhta hai wo us shakhs sey afzal hai jo buland aawaz sey Quran padhta hai, isliye ke ehle-ilm key nazdik chupa kar sadqa dena barsarey-aam sadqa deney sey afzal hai. mafhoom ye hai ke ehle-ilm key nazdik us sey aadmi ajab (khudnumaai) sey mehfooz rehta hai. kyonkey jo shakhs chupa kar amal karta hai uskey ajab mein padney ka itna khatra nahin hai jitna uskey khuley aam amal karney mein hai."
2920,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab tak Sura bani-Israel aur Sura Zumar padhna letey bistar par sotey na they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- abu-Lubaba eik Basra Shekh hain, Hammad bin Zaid ney un sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain, kaha jata hai ke unka naam Marwan hai, ye baat mujhey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney kitabut-Tarikh mein batai hai."
2921,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam soney sey pehley Musabbihat padhtey they padhi. aap farmatey they : '' un main eik aayat aisi hai jo hazar aayaton sey behtar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2922,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs subh key waqt (أعوذ بالله السميع العليم من الشيطان الرجيم) teen baar padhey, aur eik baar Sura Hashr ki aakhiri teen aayaten padhey, to Allah Taala uskey liye maghfirat maangney key liye sattar hazar farishtey laga deta hai jo Sham tak yehi kaam kartey hain. agar wo aisey din mein mar jata hai to shaheed ho kar martaa hai, aur jo shakhs un kalmaat ko Sham key waqt kaheyga wo bhi usi darjey mein hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2923,"unhoney ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz aur aap ki qirat key mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : tumhara aur aap ki namaz ka kya jod? aap namaz padhtey they phir itni der sotey they jitni der namaz padhey hotey, phir namaz padhtey they usi qadr jitni der soey huye hotey, phir itni der sotey they jitni der namaz padhey hotey. yahan tak ke aap subh kartey, phir unhoney aap key qirat ki keyfiyat bayan ki aur unhoney us keyfiyat ko wazeh taur par eik-eik harf kar key bayan kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- isey hum sirf Les bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey unhoney ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Yala bin Mamlak key wastey sey Umme-Salma sey riwayat ki, 3- ibne-Jurej ney ye hadees ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Umme-Salma sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qirat ka har harf juda hota tha, 4- Les ki hadees ( ibne-Jurej ki hadees sey) ziyada sahih hai."
2924,"mainey ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki witr key barey mein puchha ke aap witr raat key shuru hissey mein padhtey they ya aakhiri hissey mein? unhoney kaha : aap dono hi tarah sey kartey they. kabhi to aap shuru raat mein witr padh letey they aur kabhi aakhir raat mein witr padhtey they. mainey kaha : Alhamdulillah ! tamam tareef us Allah key liye hain jisney Deen key mamley mein wusat o kushadgi rakhi, phir mainey puchha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qirat kaisi hoti thi? kya aap dheerey padhtey they ya buland aawaz sey? kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye sab kartey they. kabhi to dheerey padhtey they aur kabhi aap zor sey, mainey kaha : Alhamdulillah, tamam tareefen us Allah key liye hain jisney Deen mein wusat o kushadgi rakhi. phir mainey kaha : aap jab junbi ho jatey they to kya kartey they? kya soney sey pehley ghusl kar letey they ya ghusl kiye baghair so jatey they? kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye tamam hi kartey they, kabhi to aap ghusl kar letey they phir sotey, aur kabhi wuzu kar key so jatey, mainey kaha : Allah ka shukr hai ke usney deeni kaam mein wusat o kushadgi rakhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
2925,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam « mauqif » ( Arafat ( mein apney aap ko logon key samney pesh kartey huye kehtey they : '' hai koi jo mujhey apni qom mein ley chaley, kyonkey Quraish ney mujhey apney rab key kalam (Quran) ki tableegh sey rok diya hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib sahih hai."
2926,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : jisko Quran ney meri yad ney mujh sey sawal karney sey mashghool rakha. main usey us sey ziyada dunga jitna main maangney walon ko deta hun, Allah key kalam ki fazilat doosrey sarey kalam par aisi hai jaisey Allah ki fazilat uski apni sari makhluqat par hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
